text: Come here to find nova guitar and have a stock. Good service and location. Easy to find a shop.
there are a variety of guitars to choose from and they also offer lessons, the staff are knowledgable and patient !! thankss
The location was perfect to approach and the store is very clean, and it has many different types of instrument to look at it
Visited the store today. Very friendly staff. Many types of guitar especially acoustics. Would recommend.

Tried almost every Sigma, Rainie, and Sire guitar in the store.  Before finalizing the sale, i was allowed to bring my own amplifier to try with the guitar.  Very knowledgeable, patient, considerate and kind staff.   All the best guys and thank you again!
